    "Pearcleaner and all of its files will be cleanly removed, are you sure?" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Pearcleaner和所有相关文件会被彻底删除，你确定吗？"
